			      <div type="commentary">
				        <p>Except in a brief catalog entry, this fourth Āyaka pillar from Jaggayyapeta appears to be entirely unmentioned in the literature. What remains of the text is completely parallel to EIAD <ref target="#EIAD0031">31</ref>, <ref target="#EIAD0032">32</ref> and <ref target="#EIAD0033">33</ref>. The text being intact in those inscriptions, we refer to them for a translation.</p>
			      </div>
